        <heading>3124.  Extension of time for making award</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3124.  Extension of time for making award.
Nevertheless the parties may give power to the arbitrators to prolong the time, and in this case their power lasts during the time of the prorogation.</p>
        </content>
